Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是因為構思之後的劇本而過於操勞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏和霧島同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是搞錯集合時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能幫我去看他們一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請容我重新做一次自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是一夏的姐姐 貴月繪美夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是霧島海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感謝你保護了面臨險境的一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我代表我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向你獻上誠摯的謝意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的給你添麻煩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏會由我帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發自邊境行星的求援信號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前往救援的無人飛船卻信號中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:04:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你現在別說是遇難者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可被當成失蹤了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你明白我們得知這件事後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有多擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}親戚間都引起大騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我請了帶薪假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}租了最新型的飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飛來找你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我這麼擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是你呢 輕浮的喝著小酒過著小日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至還交了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不知道會鬧得這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽起來不差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被比自己小的男孩子這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺挺新鮮的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…既然您知道一夏沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就沒問題了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經開始搜尋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但只要報告說我沒事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開發等級F
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在不允許與原住民接觸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}邊境行星上的失蹤者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從聯盟那邊看來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}必須要立即確認事態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果他們找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得知你現在的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會馬上逮捕拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}根據聯盟法予以制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼辦法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我才來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 在事情鬧大之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒辦法和海人分開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對不分開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果你執意要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會給海人還有這個星球帶來麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…又沒做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼不理解我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好聽姐姐說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你自己應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你看笑話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月…學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍攝的時間早就…過了…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼沒有穿鞋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…啊 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏同學她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論如何都得回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}得回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那比如先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後再過來之類的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在又是在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣很困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那能不能 把我也一起帶去宇宙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什麼都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像那樣既粗野又頑固的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真的覺得好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們稍稍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對我的搜索已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是那種能夠輕易逃脫的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}商量也是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}束手無策了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果非要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定會出大事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留下海人 回到宇宙去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但我已經什麼辦法都沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你就要放棄和喜歡的人在一起嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就抱著這麼輕言放棄的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過用這種程度的心意 和海人交往的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是…我是什麼感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}隨你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}輕易放棄 丟下喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼回宇宙去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這星球 真是個好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留下這麼多自然風貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明和我們的星球完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知怎的卻有種熟悉的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏同學也說過同樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這個星球上 有留於自己腦海中的印象的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才來到了這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個印象啊 在我的記憶之中也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然不能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或許那是一夏和我的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將那個印象編入遺傳基因資料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而我們繼承了它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好有埋著祖先的寶藏什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直沒在意這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但說不定 一夏她一直糾結於這個印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在尋找一夏的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我掃描了這個星球一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是卻沒有找到與印象相符的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說了想要一起去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但不能帶開發等級F的星球上的居民去宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少要等這個星球擁有能在恒星間移動的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}與我們接觸 並加入銀河聯盟為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起碼要至此 霧島同學的願望才能夠實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要到那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}以這個星球的標準時間計算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概要耗時幾百年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有沒有…有沒有什麼別的辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要聯盟法沒有被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼為一夏著想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…我會帶一夏回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是為了她好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那孩子居然有男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難得特地來接她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反倒覺得當了壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請問是貴月一夏同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐也不知道去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 海他們也是在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會是忘了要拍攝這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在親親熱熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是不是有點幸運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:10:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「是」什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海他們人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐說她要回宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說接她的人已經來了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有各種各樣的緣由什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說已經束手無策了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以電影拍攝也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}留在這裡也是浪費時間 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等啊 柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐她真的想去宇宙麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海會怎麼樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐就這樣走掉 海人被留下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣下去真的好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜你真覺得這樣好麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼可能會好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和姐姐談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我讓她把我也帶去宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}卻被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我 並沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}能和學姐在一起的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 被谷川同學罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 讓我進行跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(766,664)}jump
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:12:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 放棄的是不是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同學也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}事情的原由我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以才來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能不管啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}傷…傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.89,0:13:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}電影也拍不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我希望貴月學姐能留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡有霧島同學在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說出你的真心話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你其實想要怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不想走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想分開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡…海人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也喜歡你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}即使與宇宙為敵也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就這麼辦吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要逃走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如去哪裡藏起來之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來你們遇上麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給的你們一個喜訊吧

Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐能留在地球上？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 雖然可能性當然非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但並不是零 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}該做什麼好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 你在尋找某個留於腦海中的印象的地方是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話 我們是不是可以認為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個地球上以前也有外星人來過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但…但是 那裡不過是我的印象而已 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐的姐姐也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她腦海裡也有和學姐印象中一樣的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 她說地球上並沒有與那相似的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要在記憶中留下印象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是很費功夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說不定在那個地方 設置了不能以一夏她們的技術發現的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不就沒法調查了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.16,0:15:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}將一夏調查到的資料與地球的地圖進行對比
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對啊 如果在地圖上找到資料裡沒有的地方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬 你是怎麼想到這個的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有人給了我提示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明明說了那麼任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你得感謝你那些朋友呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒時間了 趕快行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要找到那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後那裡有地球人和外星人接觸的痕跡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}地球就不是開發等級F的行星了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果能在搜查隊到來之前能找到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 印象中的風景限定在日本當中沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 從對那之中的植物的調查情況來看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以限定在信州一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.61,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}（即是長野縣 拜託了老師的取景處）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對要找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什麼要過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從右邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海你也稍微睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 也不知道迎接學姐的人什麼時候會來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那為了打消睡意我告訴你一件好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前一段時間我向柑菜告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}騙人 那算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然結果我早已料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以你才會把谷川的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊 太過於只顧考慮自己的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以我不想你也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有呢 去沖縄的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被美櫻告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在想啊 上了高中之後什麼也沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛想做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就發生了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}尤其是從學姐來了之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個夏天真了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那可是宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然我只能做到這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是能找到就好了呢 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你的「地方」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你的「未來」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以再睡一會兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們都已經醒了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要不乾脆 我給你做膝枕？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在卿卿我我個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找…找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒被檢查過的地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏 能聽到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搜查隊在星球附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快從…那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 快讓我們跳躍到剛才找到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會…反連環力場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(722,664)}linkage anti-field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}籠罩著整個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無法傳送
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 就算是坐電車去也要花3小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}追兵不是要來了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不快點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無人駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我早料到會有這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提前準備了車真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 你有駕駛證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會派什麼人來接你？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概會和之前一樣是救援飛船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對方會通過搜索你的生物資料而來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 但為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}披上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會將你放出的生物反應減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}按下開關之後會產生和一夏的生物資料一樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道這也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 是受你姐姐幫助而得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好 就這樣一口氣到達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在嘎吱嘎吱的響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}追兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定要到達那裡啊 海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來吧來吧 快靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}BINGO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下次啊 不去看電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有柑菜和海 就我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恩 去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走75號線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.64,0:21:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剩下的 還有10公里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是為了學姐才這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是為了我最喜歡的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為想要我最喜歡的人保持著微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}三年之後 會讓你後悔死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要幸福啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像…沒有追兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明擺著的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拍攝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.57,0:21:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}主角一邊受到敵人攻擊一邊向目的地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.77,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像能拍出很棒的高潮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.12,0:22:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後結尾就交給神明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這也是拍攝電影的妙趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.56,0:22:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}準備OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好 開拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.13,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}纏人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.09,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:34.99,副本Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這車

